    {
      "index": 5,
      "heading": "Grow as a #ConfidentConsultant",
      "text": "Expanding my Salesforce knowledge and customer relationship skills continue to be so important, for both my professional and personal life. Because I’m a lifelong learner, I was able to grow my career and land my dream role as a#ConfidentConsultant. Now, I strive to provide the best expertise and solutions for customers to be successful. I consider my journey as a Salesforce consultant just the beginning. With every new customer comes a new challenge with new skills to learn and new solutions to uncover. That’s why I love being a Salesforce consultant—every project is unique and different. This variety allows me to continuously grow and, more importantly, better support my customers. Check out my favorite resources: Trailhead:Salesforce Consultant Career PathTrailhead:SalesforceConsultantCertificationsTrailhead:Functional Consultant TrailmixSalesforce Partners:Salesforce Talent AllianceSalesforce Partners:#AlwaysBeLearning BlogAppExchange:Deloitte Digital Follow Marvin on the Trailblazer Community attrailblazer.me/id/marvincross.",
